Television presenter and actress Palesa Tembe has announced that she is now officially off the market. Tembe is the sister of the late Anele ‘Nellie’ Tembe [fiancé to the late Kiernan ‘AKA’ Forbes]. She said Mandlenkosi Ngubane came to pay lobola over the weekend. “Someone’s uncles came to my parent’s gate this morning,” she wrote. Her best friend and The Wife actress, Mbalenhle Mavimbela, congratulated the presenter on her new journey.  For the latest entertainment news from Sunday World, click here. Or read the latest from Shwashwi here. Follow @SundayWorldZA on Twitter and @sundayworldza on Instagram, or like our Facebook Page, Sunday World, by clicking here for the latest breaking news in South Africa. To Subscribe to Sunday World, click here